1	//! `LanceDB` storage layer.
2	//!
3	//! Embedded columnar + vector database running inside the Rust process.
4	//! Zero network, zero config — reads/writes Arrow columns directly.
5	//!
6	//! Responsibilities:
7	//! - [`DecisionRecord`] CRUD with vector indexing (cosine similarity)
8	//! - Goal state persistence (crash recovery)
9	//! - Session history archival
10	//! - `IVF_PQ` index for sub-20ms search at 1M+ records
11	
